			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Cast this when root runs out on a mummy or skel and then whack him in the back while he runs away-with a nice weapon and high skill, worth 60-80 extra dmg with no dmg to yourself. Works great with yellows and below. Resisted a lot on reds.
