	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				An invaluable spell to have. Still used at lvl 23 because of its effectiveness and low mana consumption, Spook can save you time and mana when fighting the undead. While pulling undead mobs, they will pickup any of there undead friends to join the ride and give a little run for your money. Cast Spook on one and it will give you about a good 45 seconds of free time to deal with Enemy #1. Also a great spell to have if you are fighting an undead foe that has gotten the best of you and you have limited mana. Spook him and run for the closest zone. Better than any root or stun spell. The only downfall is that 9 times out of 10, he will be back, and in full force with a few friends, madder than hell. So make sure theres a zone nearby.<BR>
<BR>
Meleen Dearado<BR>
Cleric of Rodect Nife<BR>
23rd Season<BR>
Quellious
