			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is one fun spell!  Im a High Elf Cleric, and I use it in a totally un-cleric way.  If you really want to find undead guys (since we are so good against them) and there is a shortage of them, and you see somebody else fighting one, cast this.  The undead monster runs away, then you pelt if with Strike (and others), if you dont kill it then, who cares! It comes back at you!  Heh heh heh, its mean, but hey, it works.<BR>
